ion api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Systems.Configuration.Graphic.IGraphicSetting.GridColor' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Ecs.Systems.Configuration.Graphic.IGraphicSetting.GridColor' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Systems_Configuration_Graphic_IGraphicSetting_GridColor'>GridColor    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/2_Application/Alis/src/Core/Ecs/Systems/Configuration/Graphic/IGraphicSetting.cs#L58'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Systems.Configuration.Graphic.IGraphicSetting.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets or sets the value of the grid color</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>Color GridColor { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='Alis.Core.Aspect.Math.Definition.Color.html'>Color</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Systems.Configuration.Graphic.IGraphicSetting.HasGrid' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Ecs.Systems.Configuration.Graphic.IGraphicSetting.HasGrid' id='Alis_Core_Ecs_Systems_Configuration_Graphic_IGraphicSetting_HasGrid'>HasGrid    <a class='header-action link-secondary' title='View source' href='https://github.com/pabllopf/Alis/blob/master/2_Application/Alis/src/Core/Ecs/Systems/Configuration/Graphic/IGraphicSetting.cs#L63'><i class='bi bi-code-slash'></i></a></h3>\r\n <p sourceFile=\"api/Alis.Core.Ecs.Systems.Configuration.Graphic.IGraphicSetting.yml\" sourceStartLineNumber=\"1\">Gets or sets the value of the has grid</p>\n<pre><code class='lang-csharp'>bool HasGrid { get; set; }</code></pre><h4 class='section'>Property Value</h4><dl class='parameters'><dt> <a href='https://learn.microsoft.com/dotnet/api/system.boolean'>bool</a>  </dt>\r\n<dd>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</dd></dl><h3 class='section api' data-uid='Alis.Core.Ecs.Systems.Configuration.Graphic.IGraphicSetting.IsResizable' data-commentId='P:Alis.Core.Ecs.Systems.Configuration.